keyInstructions.setupInfo:
To use the CoinGecko Pro API SDK:

1. Sign up for a CoinGecko Pro account at https://www.coingecko.com/en/api/pricing
2. Once subscribed, obtain your API key from the CoinGecko dashboard
3. Set your API key as an environment variable:
   export COINGECKO_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
4. Alternatively, you can pass the API key directly when initializing the SDK

Usage example:

```typescript
import { createCoinGeckoSDK } from '@microfox/coingecko-api';

// Using environment variable
const sdk = createCoinGeckoSDK();

// Or passing the API key directly
const sdk = createCoinGeckoSDK({ apiKey: 'your_api_key_here' });

// Make API calls
const bitcoinPrice = await sdk.getSimplePrice({ ids: 'bitcoin', vs_currencies: 'usd' });
console.log(bitcoinPrice);
```

Note: This SDK is for the Pro API, which requires a paid subscription. Ensure you have an active subscription before using this SDK.
